sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Server as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant AuthMW as Authentication MW<br/>(OAuth2 JWT / Custom)
    participant ACMW as Access Control MW<br/>(Cedar ABAC)
    participant QuotaMW as Quota MW
    participant OIDC as OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant InfRouter as Inference Router
    participant AgentProv as Agent Provider<br/>(in-process)
    participant vLLM as vLLM Backend<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant RAGTool as RAG Tool Runtime<br/>(in-process)
    participant PgVector as PostgreSQL pgvector<br/>5432/TCP
    participant SafetyRouter as Safety Router
    participant OTel as OTel Collector<br/>OTLP HTTP

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 1: Chat Completion Request

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/inference/chat-completion<br/>Auth: Bearer <JWT>
    Server->>AuthMW: Validate token
    AuthMW->>OIDC: GET /.well-known/jwks.json<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    OIDC-->>AuthMW: JWKS public keys
    AuthMW->>AuthMW: Verify JWT signature<br/>Extract claims (sub, groups, roles)
    AuthMW->>ACMW: Pass authenticated request<br/>with principal attributes
    ACMW->>ACMW: Evaluate Cedar policies<br/>permit/forbid rules
    ACMW->>QuotaMW: Authorized request
    QuotaMW->>QuotaMW: Check rate limit<br/>(1000 req/day authenticated)
    QuotaMW->>InfRouter: Route to inference provider
    InfRouter->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Bearer Token
    vLLM-->>InfRouter: Completion response (SSE stream)
    InfRouter-->>Server: Stream response
    Server->>OTel: Export trace spans<br/>OTLP HTTP
    Server-->>Client: SSE stream response<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Configurable TLS

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 2: Agent Turn with RAG Tool Use

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/agents/{id}/turn<br/>Auth: Bearer <JWT>
    Server->>AuthMW: Validate token
    AuthMW-->>ACMW: Authenticated
    ACMW-->>QuotaMW: Authorized
    QuotaMW->>AgentProv: Route to agent provider

    AgentProv->>InfRouter: Initial chat-completion<br/>(in-process call)
    InfRouter->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Bearer Token
    vLLM-->>InfRouter: Response with tool_call<br/>(RAG query needed)
    InfRouter-->>AgentProv: Tool call response

    AgentProv->>RAGTool: Execute RAG query<br/>(in-process)
    RAGTool->>PgVector: SELECT with vector similarity<br/>TCP/5432, Configurable TLS<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    PgVector-->>RAGTool: Relevant documents
    RAGTool-->>AgentProv: RAG context

    AgentProv->>InfRouter: Chat-completion with context<br/>(in-process call)
    InfRouter->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Bearer Token
    vLLM-->>InfRouter: Final response
    InfRouter-->>AgentProv: Completion

    AgentProv-->>Server: Agent turn result
    Server->>OTel: Export trace spans
    Server-->>Client: SSE stream response

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 3: Safety Shield Execution

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/safety/run-shield<br/>Auth: Bearer <JWT>
    Server->>AuthMW: Validate token
    AuthMW-->>ACMW: Authenticated
    ACMW-->>QuotaMW: Authorized
    QuotaMW->>SafetyRouter: Route to safety provider
    SafetyRouter->>vLLM: Inference request (Llama Guard)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Bearer Token
    vLLM-->>SafetyRouter: Safety classification
    SafetyRouter-->>Server: Shield result (safe/unsafe)
    Server-->>Client: Shield response<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
